name: CI Marret Alternative Absolute Return Bond Fund
longDescription: The fund seeks to provide positive absolute returns with low volatility over a market cycle regardless of market conditions or general market direction, by primarily investing in debt instruments across the credit spectrum including cash, government debt, investment grade corporate debt, high yield debt, credit derivatives and other income-producing securities throughout the world. The fund will invest primarily in debt instruments across the credit spectrum including cash, government debt, investment grade corporate debt, convertible bonds, high yield debt, government agency securities, inflation-linked bonds, private debt, credit derivatives and other income-producing securities throughout the world.
